title: Whats the hold up with the program skins?
body: Patch was 9 days ago. The skins are already patched in. If I was a writing I could not write a good reason for them not to be out other than people forgot to hit the button. At this point you might as well have just said you were going to release them during 8.23.

replies.body: I think they just came out this minute actually lol
They just released the Fiddle and Graves skin not long ago. They don't like skins overlapping others. More then likely it will be out later today or Monday.
